@startuml component_architecture
!theme plain

title UIM Document Management Integration Service — Component Architecture

actor "Business App\n(SAP Fiori / Custom)" as App
actor "End User\n(Embedded UI5 Component)" as User
actor "Admin / Operator" as Admin

node "Document Management Integration Service Runtime" {
    component "DocMgmtIntegrationServer\n(vibe.d REST API)" as Api
    component "DocMgmtIntegrationService\n(Tenant-Scoped Business Logic)" as Domain
    component "EncryptionManager\n(XOR-SHA256-derived)" as Crypto
    component "RepositoryRegistry\n(Tenant-Scoped Connectors)" as Registry
    database "DocMgmtIntegrationStore\n(In-Memory: Tenants,\nDocs, Folders, Versions,\nLinks, UI Configs)" as Store
}

cloud "External CMIS Repository\n(On-Premise / Cloud)" as ExtRepo

App --> Api : Integration APIs\n(tenant-scoped CRUD)
User --> Api : Embedded UI5 component\ncalls via REST
Admin --> Api : Tenant mgmt,\nEncryption config
Api --> Domain : route + validate\n+ extract tenantId
Domain --> Crypto : encrypt / decrypt content
Domain --> Registry : connect / list repos\n(per tenant)
Domain --> Store : persist / read / move / copy\n(tenant-isolated)
Registry --> ExtRepo : CMIS AtomPub binding

note right of Domain
  Integration Features:
  - Multi-tenant isolation
  - Tenant CRUD lifecycle
  - Integration Links
    (bind external business objects)
  - Embeddable UI5 component config
  - File & Folder CRUD
  - Breadcrumb navigation
  - Move & Copy operations
  - Document versioning
  - Check-out / Check-in workflow
  - Metadata management
  - Encryption at rest
  - CMIS repository support
  - Sorting / personalisation
end note

@enduml
